Package es.tid.rsvp.constructs

RSVP Constructs as described in both RFC 2205 and RFC 3209

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ErrorFlowDescriptor
    Represents a Error Flow Descriptor construct, as defined in RFC 2205.
    FFErrorFlowDescriptor
    Represents a FF Style Error Flow Descriptor construct, as defined in RFC 2205.
    FFFlowDescriptor
    Represents a FF Style Flow Descriptor construct, as defined in RFC 2205.
    FlowDescriptor
    Represents a Flow Descriptor construct, as defined in RFC 2205.
    RSVPConstruct
    A RSVP Construct is a rule that joins RSVP Objects and Constructions.

    Represents a SE Style Error Flow Descriptor construct, as defined in RFC 2205.

    Represents a WF Style Error Flow Descriptor construct, as defined in RFC 2205.
